@description: Feet per hour per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [fph/s]. Definition of 1 feet per hour per second ≡ 1 ft/(h·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 fph velocity in 1 second..

Feet per minute per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [fpm/s]. Definition of 1 feet per minute per second ≡ 1 ft/(min·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 fpm velocity in 1 second..
Feet per second squared is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [fps²]. Definition of 1 feet per second squared ≡ 1 ft/s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 fps velocity in 1 second..
Galileo is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [Gal]. Definition of 1 galileo ≡ 1 cm/s². Acceleration unit named after Galileo Galilei, value is exactly 1 cm/s².

Inches per hour per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [iph/s]. Definition of 1 inches per hour per second ≡ 1 in/(h·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 iph velocity in 1 second..

Inches per minute per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [ipm/s]. Definition of 1 inches per minute per second ≡ 1 in/(min·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 ipm velocity in 1 second..
Inches per second squared is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [ips²]. Definition of 1 inches per second squared ≡ 1 in/s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 ips velocity in 1 second..

Kilometres per hour per second is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [km/(h·s)]. Definition of 1 kilometres per hour per second ≡ 1000 m / 3600 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 km/h velocity in 1 second..

Kilometres per minute per second is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [km/(min·s)]. Definition of 1 kilometres per minute per second ≡ 1000 m / 60 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 km/min velocity in 1 second..

Kilometres per second squared is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [km/s²]. Definition of 1 kilometres per second squared ≡ 1000 m / 1 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 km/s velocity in 1 second..
Knots per second is acceleration unit, symbol: [kn/s]. Definition of 1 knots per second ≡ 1 kn/s. Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 knot velocity in 1 second..

Metres per hour per second is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [m/(h·s)]. Definition of 1 metres per hour per second ≡ 1 m / 3600 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 m/h velocity in 1 second..

Metres per minute per second is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [m/(min·s)]. Definition of 1 metres per minute per second ≡ 1 m / 60 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 m/min velocity in 1 second..
Metres per second squared is Metric acceleration unit, symbol: [m/s²]. Definition of 1 metres per second squared ≡ 1 m / 1 s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 m/s velocity in 1 second..

Miles per hour per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [mph/s]. Definition of 1 miles per hour per second ≡ 1 mi/(h·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 mph velocity in 1 second..

Miles per minute per second is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [mpm/s]. Definition of 1 miles per minute per second ≡ 1 mi/(min·s). Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 mpm velocity in 1 second..
Miles per second squared is British/American acceleration unit, symbol: [mps²]. Definition of 1 miles per second squared ≡ 1 mi/s². Acceleration equivalent to change of 1 mps velocity in 1 second..
